673
00:40:38,510 --> 00:40:41,070
Then the evil object was sent to Yunzhou.

674
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:42,800
After all that happened,

675
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:46,190
Lord Wei must've figured out your goal.

676
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:47,880
Never mind.

677
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,030
He's

678
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:52,440
